com.sap.cloud.sdk.services.recastai

Class NlpResponseWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.services.recastai.NlpResponseWrapper

  • @Beta
public class NlpResponseWrapper
extends Object
    Wraps around text data to be sent to recast for a nlp analysis. This object is used in combination with RecastAnalyser.

    Be aware that this class is in Beta (as indicated by the annotation) and therefore subject to breaking changes.
